title: Heritage
description: Experience the elegance of tradition with warm, muted tones and classic design elements. Ideal for surveys with a timeless feel.

title: Simple
description: Embrace minimalism with a clean, straightforward layout. Perfect for content-focused surveys where clarity is key.

title: Full Color
description: Dive into a world of vibrant colors! This lively theme adds energy and fun to your surveys.

title: Highrise
description: Capture the essence of the modern cityscape with sleek lines and urban-inspired colors. Great for professional and contemporary surveys.

title: Dewdrop
description: Enjoy the freshness of early morning with soft blues and greens, and a tranquil, nature-inspired design.

title: Pastel
description: Soft and soothing, this theme uses gentle pastels for a calming survey experience.

title: Walnut
description: Rich walnut textures and warm brown tones bring a natural and trustworthy feel to your surveys.

title: Stone
description: Cool, muted colors and stone-like textures offer a strong, stable backdrop for your questions.

title: Porch Lights
description: Feel the warmth and welcome of a cozy porch with this homely and inviting theme.

title: Scribble
description: Fun and spontaneous, this theme features bright colors and playful, hand-drawn designs.

title: Arctic
description: Crisp and cool, the Arctic theme uses icy blues and whites for a clean, sharp look.
